title: SEAFORT ORB / full faln set
description: test case orb for wearing the full faln set if you have all of the items.

dialogueTree.title: Composure: "O glorious Falnier! You wear the fu..."
dialogueTree.english: O glorious Falnier! You wear the full set like a true-born hero. The *ULTIMATE PERFORMANCE* of FALN flows in you.
dialogueTree.polish: O, wielki falnowcu! Nosisz ten pełny zestaw niczym urodzony bohater. *IDEALNA WYDAJNOŚĆ* FALN płynie w twoich żyłach.
dialogueTree.belarusian: О, вялікі фалноўцу! Носіш гэты поўны камплект, як народжаны герой. *ІДЭАЛЬНАЯ ВЫДАЙНАСЦЬ* ФАЛН цячэ ў тваіх жылах.

links.title: Composure: "You are the most *Ultra* of men. Pe..."
links.english: You are the most *Ultra* of men. Peak performance!

links.title: Composure: "Go on! The fucking sunset awaits, F..."
links.english: Go on! The fucking sunset awaits, FALN rider!
links.polish: Ruszaj, jeźdźcze FALN! Jebany zachód słońca czeka!
links.belarusian: Наперад, вершнік ФАЛН! Чортавы захад сонца чакае!

links.title: Composure: "You are Next Century personified, t..."
links.english: You are Next Century personified, the synthetic man!
links.polish: Jesteś uosobieniem kolejnego stulecia. Syntetycznym człowiekiem!
links.belarusian: Вы ўвасабляеце сабой наступнае стагоддзе. Сінтэтычная чалавек!

links.title: You: "It's like I can do anything. *ANYTH..."
links.english: It's like I can do anything. *ANYTHING*!
links.polish: Jakbym mógł zrobić, co zechcę. *CO ZECHCĘ*!
links.belarusian: Каб я мог зрабіць, што захачу. *ШТО ЗАХАЧУ*!

links.title: Composure: "You are literally untouchable. A go..."
links.english: You are literally untouchable. A god among mere men.
links.polish: Jesteś dosłownie nietykalny. Niczym bóg pośród zwykłych ludzi.
links.belarusian: Вы літаральна недатыкальны. Так, як бог сярод звычайных людзей.
